Package io.micronaut.nats.jetstream.annotation

Annotation Interface PushConsumer

@Documented @Retention(RUNTIME) @Target({METHOD,PARAMETER,TYPE}) @Bindable @Executable @MessageMapping @Inherited public @interface PushConsumer
Used to specify which stream should be used for messages.
Since:
4.0.0
Author:
Joachim Grimm
